Package: crownsegmentr
Title: Tree Crown Segmentation in Airborne LiDAR Point Clouds
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c( person("Leon", "Steinmeier", ,
        "Leon.Steinmeier@posteo.net", role = "aut", comment = c(ORCID =
        "0000-0001-9040-636X", "Created the package as part of his
