Maintainer: Timon Miesner <timon.miesner@thuenen.de>
Description: Provides a function that performs the adaptive mean shift
        algorithm for individual tree crown delineation in 3D point
        clouds as proposed by Ferraz et al. (2016)
        <doi:10.1016/j.rse.2016.05.028>, as well as supporting
        functions.
